    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217050/extras/691d0120baa65ad8ac706dc4bbac6976.avif?t=1764777664\" width=1200 height=156 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217050/extras/913427e79facb809645c996355455870.poster.avif?t=1764777664\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217050/extras/913427e79facb809645c996355455870.webm?t=1764777664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217050/extras/913427e79facb809645c996355455870.mp4?t=1764777664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Assist customers by scanning movies, taking payments, and managing returns, to grow your retro video rental store!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217050/extras/b4f8ff123895a26c9b89a383fecbd362.avif?t=1764777664\" width=1200 height=156 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217050/extras/03b9b0e89531f946c10099e44e257a56.poster.avif?t=1764777664\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217050/extras/03b9b0e89531f946c10099e44e257a56.webm?t=1764777664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217050/extras/03b9b0e89531f946c10099e44e257a56.mp4?t=1764777664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose which movies to sell, and place them within your store. As you progress you can unlock consoles, video players, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217050/extras/b058130891cbead96f94e21b35247606.avif?t=1764777664\" width=1200 height=156 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217050/extras/65a80b8740d3bc3565e114304bd40bc4.poster.avif?t=1764777664\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217050/extras/65a80b8740d3bc3565e114304bd40bc4.webm?t=1764777664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217050/extras/65a80b8740d3bc3565e114304bd40bc4.mp4?t=1764777664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep on top of it! Scrub graffiti, pick up trash, and sweep leaves to keep your store looking tidy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217050/extras/4874475846cba3d64c42e0be2d9a2a45.avif?t=1764777664\" width=1200 height=156 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217050/extras/d70748ac6e9c2101bdbc35b1f484e976.avif?t=1764777664\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your store, unlock more products, hire employees, attract more customers and boost your business!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217050/extras/f4697d7c0d2de374d7aed260a77593ec.avif?t=1764777664\" width=1200 height=156 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217050/extras/7f728ce139cb18848be6ef7170e67e99.avif?t=1764777664\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock a range of customization options and change the look and feel of your store. Find what suits you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase movies, consoles, video players, and snacks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rent them to customers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Process returns</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clean up the store</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Handle cash and card payments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your store</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hire employees</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decorate</p></li></ul>",
